snippet.title: Jorōgumo - じょろうぐも // Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2442760/Jorgumo/

Embark on a perilous journey through the haunting depths of the forest in Jorogumo, a gripping stealth and puzzle game. When your brother vanishes in the eerie woods, you must summon your courage and venture into the heart of darkness to unravel the enigma surrounding the ancient legend of Jorogumo.

Developed by
Nyxtales
